author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Commonwealth Bank Of Australia Acknowledges Release Of Progress Report By Prudential Inquiry Panel
text:
Feb 1 (Reuters) - Commonwealth Bank Of Australia:
* RESPONSE TO PRUDENTIAL INQUIRY PANEL PROGRESS REPORT * ACKNOWLEDGES RELEASE OF PROGRESS REPORT BY PRUDENTIAL INQUIRY PANEL
* ‍COOPERATING FULLY WITH INQUIRY AND WELCOME OPPORTUNITY FOR PANEL TO REVIEW WORK WE HAVE UNDERTAKEN​
* PANEL‘S FINAL REPORT, WHICH WILL OUTLINE FINDINGS AND RECOMMENDATIONS, IS EXPECTED BY END OF APRIL 2018 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
